item.title: ⚡MINI: Hayley & Max Do A Séance Live On Air
item.description:
Are you brave enough to tune in for a paranormal radio experience? Join Max & Hayley and resident spiritual guide Luna Luke as they attempt to contact the other side in Mix102.3's first-ever radio séance. What begins as a lighthearted studio experiment quickly takes an unexpected turn when the team notices flickering candles and strange sensations after calling upon spirits to make their presence known.
